      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRUST A PROCESS (1) is long overdue and boasts a solid record despite not having won his maiden yet, the latest finishing second at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from three attempts. One of the leading chances. DALAIR MILO (8) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 2.5 lengths into second (20.01) at this track in a Maiden over 340m. Can measure up. GO FORWARD BERNY (2) is still a maiden after eight runs but rarely far away, the latest finishing out of the placings when fifth at Dubbo. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. HOOLIGAN MOLLY (7) makes debut for the Kevin Sills kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles well so watch market closely.",
